{"tid":940455,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南京大屠殺公祭日　網民稱「買日貨壓驚」捱轟遭解僱","createTime":"2018-12-14T02:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T03:17:45.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"97365bc380553f760c18d844bb521ee776d32757","tid":940455,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181214/s00004/a968f47d04b381790190c9f4644a4216.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181214%2Fs00004%2Fa968f47d04b381790190c9f4644a4216.jpg&h=4529a2e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨天（13日）為南京大屠殺81周年，也是首天實行《南京市國家公祭保障條例》，一名網民在微信朋友圈發文稱：「都在默哀，嚇死我了！買點日貨壓壓驚」，相關截圖在網上廣傳，被批評為不尊重死難者；雖然她之後致歉，但其僱主「和信貸」在微博上發聲明解僱她。執法機構目前尚未介入事件。<br />\n<br />\n2014年2月全國人大常委會通過將每年的12月13日定為「南京大屠殺死難者國家公祭日」。今年11月南京市通過《國家公祭保障條例》，昨日為法例施行的首日，禁止「精日」行為，執法機關可追究刑事責任。所謂「精日」分子，是指「精神上將自己等同於日本（極右翼）的人」。<br />\n<br />\n在南京大屠殺公祭日於網上發文稱要買日貨壓驚的微信帳戶名為「和信貸經理顧某某」，結果招來圍攻批評，有人斥責她「沒有國家意識」，「拿着民族傷疤開玩笑，以為自己很幽默」。直至昨日中午，涉事人在朋友圈致歉，指言論的原意是諷刺一些默哀時還使用日貨、駕駛日產汽車的人，卻因自己前後沒說清楚招來公眾誤解，已作深刻檢討。<br />\n<br />\n然而，顧的解釋及道歉未能平息網民不滿，她所屬公司「和信貸」微博昨午及晚上發聲明，表示顧的「不良言論」屬個人行為，公司已辭退她，強調公司將進一步加強員工思想教育工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20181214/s00004/1544752141369/南京大屠殺公祭日-網民稱「買日貨壓驚」捱轟遭解僱\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20181214%2Fs00004%2F1544752141369%2F%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%A0%E6%AE%BA%E5%85%AC%E7%A5%AD%E6%97%A5-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%A8%B1%E3%80%8C%E8%B2%B7%E6%97%A5%E8%B2%A8%E5%A3%93%E9%A9%9A%E3%80%8D%E6%8D%B1%E8%BD%9F%E9%81%AD%E8%A7%A3%E5%83%B1&d=1zEXC4gEBXXb6dtK4q2adeI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=395f0943\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20181214%2Fs00004%2F1544752141369%2F%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%A4%A7%E5%B1%A0%E6%AE%BA%E5%85%AC%E7%A5%AD%E6%97%A5-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%A8%B1%E3%80%8C%E8%B2%B7%E6%97%A5%E8%B2%A8%E5%A3%93%E9%A9%9A%E3%80%8D%E6%8D%B1%E8%BD%9F%E9%81%AD%E8%A7%A3%E5%83%B1&h=c710e9bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20181214/s00004/1544752141369/南京大屠殺公祭日-網民稱「買日貨壓驚」捱轟遭解僱</a>"},{"pid":"a4b43d9e53ea3ca7a04e2611fe2c9a90e8bf1d55","tid":940455,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T03:00:54.000Z","msg":"Onll99"},{"pid":"dfe872ea6a98e942c911002bdacec7a1ca8c0af9","tid":940455,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T03:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K5Vm3KK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK5Vm3KK.gif&h=cb49f939&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98b669b89cbd2c74c7246c4a2bea7ff67e19fa16","tid":940455,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T03:07:22.000Z","msg":"生喺鬼國仲敢講真話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20581df8e38036739ade9e40ef2900dae4e2bc2","tid":940455,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T03:08:19.000Z","msg":"Oppa Chi Na Style<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdab3bcd0b89b15ab22aa99b7e3433e254d2db97","tid":940455,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T03:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}